{"title": "Gobuster", "source": "enum", "source_label": "Enumeration", "path": "gobuster", "html": "<h1 id=\"gobuster\">Gobuster</h1>\n<h2 id=\"dir-mode\">Dir Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic directory brute force</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With file extensions</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>php,html,txt,bak,old\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Follow redirects</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Increase threads</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Ignore SSL errors</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show status codes in output</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,301,302,403\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Hide specific status codes</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>,500\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Output to file</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>gobuster_dir.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With proxy</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--proxy<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://127.0.0.1:8080\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Add trailing slash to attempts</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-f\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Expanded output (show lengths, status, etc.)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-e\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter by length</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--exclude-length<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Timeout per request</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--timeout<span class=\"w\"> </span>10s\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Delay between requests (rate limit)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--delay<span class=\"w\"> </span>50ms\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># User agent</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Mozilla/5.0&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Verbose (show all attempts)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># No error output</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--no-error\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># No progress bar</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-z\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"dir-mode-authentication\">Dir Mode — Authentication</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Basic auth</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-U<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;username&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-P<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;password&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Cookie authentication</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-c<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;session=abc123&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Bearer token</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Authorization: Bearer &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Multiple headers</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Authorization: Bearer &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;X-Custom-Header: value&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API key</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;X-Api-Key: &lt;password&gt;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"dir-mode-common-patterns\">Dir Mode — Common Patterns</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># PHP application</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>php,html,txt,bak<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># ASP.NET application</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>aspx,asp,html,txt,config<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Quick initial recon</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">40</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Sensitive file hunt</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>bak,old,zip,tar.gz,sql,conf,config,env,log\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Recursive (manual chaining)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/admin<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"dns-mode\">DNS Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Subdomain enumeration</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Show IP addresses</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom DNS resolver</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-r<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">8</span>.8.8.8\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Output</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>subdomains.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Threads</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Include wildcard results (show even if wildcard exists)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--wildcard\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Verbose (show CNAMEs)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-v\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Timeout</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--timeout<span class=\"w\"> </span>5s\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"vhost-mode\">VHost Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Virtual host enumeration</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Append domain automatically</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--append-domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter false positives by length</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>--exclude-length<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1234</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With HTTPS (ignore cert)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>https://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-k\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Threads + output</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhosts.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Custom User-Agent</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-a<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Mozilla/5.0&quot;</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With domain appended manually in wordlist</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-H<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;Host: FUZZ.&lt;domain&gt;&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"fuzz-mode\">Fuzz Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Generic fuzzing (any position)</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>fuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Fuzz GET parameter</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>fuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s2\">&quot;&lt;url&gt;?id=FUZZ&quot;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Fuzz with extensions in FUZZ</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>fuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Filter responses</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>fuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span>,403<span class=\"w\"> </span>--exclude-length<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">0</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Match status codes</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>fuzz<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/FUZZ<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"s3-mode\">S3 Mode</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># AWS S3 bucket enumeration</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>s3<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># With threads</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>s3<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Output</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>s3<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>s3_buckets.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"pattern-files\">Pattern Files</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Use a pattern file to append to wordlist entries</span>\n<span class=\"c1\"># Create pattern file:</span>\ncat<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>patterns.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&lt;&lt; &#39;EOF&#39;</span>\n<span class=\"s\">{GOBUSTER}/v1</span>\n<span class=\"s\">{GOBUSTER}/v2</span>\n<span class=\"s\">{GOBUSTER}/api</span>\n<span class=\"s\">{GOBUSTER}/backup</span>\n<span class=\"s\">EOF</span>\n\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;wordlist&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>patterns.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Pattern for API versioning</span>\ncat<span class=\"w\"> </span>&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>api_patterns.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">&lt;&lt; &#39;EOF&#39;</span>\n<span class=\"s\">/api/{GOBUSTER}</span>\n<span class=\"s\">/api/v1/{GOBUSTER}</span>\n<span class=\"s\">/api/v2/{GOBUSTER}</span>\n<span class=\"s\">EOF</span>\n\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/common.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>api_patterns.txt\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"practical-one-liners\">Practical One-Liners</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\"># Fast full recon</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-medium-directories.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">40</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>/tmp/gobuster_&lt;target&gt;.txt\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># Subdomain + vhost combo</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dns<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>-i\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>vhost<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>http://&lt;ip&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/DNS/subdomains-top1million-5000.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span>--append-domain<span class=\"w\"> </span>-d<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;domain&gt;\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># API fuzzing</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;/api<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/api/api-endpoints.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-s<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,201,204,400,401,403,405<span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">30</span>\n\n<span class=\"c1\"># File hunt with extensions</span>\ngobuster<span class=\"w\"> </span>dir<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;url&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-w<span class=\"w\"> </span>/usr/share/seclists/Discovery/Web-Content/raft-large-files.txt<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-x<span class=\"w\"> </span>php,txt,html,bak,old,zip,sql,conf,log,env<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"se\">\\</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>-b<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">404</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-t<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">50</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-o<span class=\"w\"> </span>files.txt\n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Gobuster Dir Mode # Basic directory brute force gobuster dir -u &lt;url&gt; -w &lt;wordlist&gt; # With file extensions gobuster dir -u &lt;url&gt; -w &lt;wordlist&gt; -x php,html,txt,bak,old # Follow ", "tags": []}